highlights.text: “Take My Breath - Single Version” by The Weeknd is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #7.
Billie Eilish has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Happier Than Ever” is the highest at #6.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 236 weeks straight.
